data.description: This cozy brick home has 3 bedrooms and one full bathroom, living room, extended eat in kitchen, kitchen appliances stay with home plus washer and dryer.  This home sits on a small level yard with a storage shed and paved driveway; heat pump and water heater were installed in 2020; home has walk in shower that was installed in 2021, backup heat source -  gas heater installed in 2022;  This home is about one mile from the LMU Ewing Vet Campus.
